args: The beef has been cut into 36 equal\nportions. The margin of error was\nless than 1%.
Indeed. Ranzal should have no complaints\nabout whatever slice he receives.
I require no thanks. It is my duty to serve.
Yes, well... Let's get this cooking,\nshall we?
My body has adjusted to the replacement\nparts that were installed after I went\nout of control.
The only parts left to confirm are...
So the Empire has finally moved to take\nMyriage Lake?
Yeah, and I'm gonna stop 'em!\nNobody messes with my homeland!
As soon as our scouts return with word on\ntheir numbers, we'll lead a force there.
I have no idea. She showed up suddenly\nand started ordering the other androids\ninto a line.
Their presence has completely impeded\nmy hanging of the laundry.
Whoa... You were gonna hang all\nthis yourself?
You really do too much for us, Cleo.
What's up, Laxi? Are you training the\nother androids?
They do not require training.\nI am performing self-maintenance.

I desired to confirm whether I could still
transmit orders as their commander.
No notable errors have been detected
thus far.
I can now confirm that all my previously\ndamaged parts have been fixed\nsuccessfully. I am cleared for combat.
Er, are you planning to fight someone?
Of course. It is my purpose for being.
I understand that, but I invited you here\nto show you a more peaceful life.
I don't want you to feel compelled to fight.
I am...confused. Is a peaceful life not\nclaimed through combat?
Well, I guess they're somewhat related,\nbut... Mascula doesn't want to fight, right?
▷Correct. But I'm afraid Laxi doesn't\npay much mind to my desires.◁
There is no need to.\n▷See? She won't budge.◁\nI am simply being practical.
*ahem* So, your maintenance is done?\nThat's good to hear.
In that case, could you send the other\nandroids back to their rooms so Cleo\ncan finish hanging the laundry?
Or... Maybe you can all work\ntogether to help her?
▷We'd be happy to.◁\nAll units, hang the washing.
Mascula was always strange,\nbut Laxi's on a totally different\nlevel. She's so...bossy.
Yeah... I hope the two of them can learn\nto compromise.
Use clothespins, please.\nThe wind is quite strong today.
▷Laxi, there's something I want to\nmake clear.◁
▷I may not have my own body to make\nuse of anymore, but I haven't given up\non my dream.◁
▷I'm going to keep fighting, however I\ncan, until you walk away from combat.◁
You contradict yourself. How can you fight\nif you're avoiding fighting?
▷You don't need to understand. Just know\nthat as long as you keep fighting, I will\nwork to stop you.◁
That's simply impossible.\n▷I guess we'll see, won't we?◁
